    narr:generatedFrom "d1b09a828565de86" ;
    narr:narration """This hub gathers per-document/per-transcript **phrasing** assessments from a writing rubric. The dominant finding repeats across nearly every child: a **strong idiolect** built from domain verbs and signature stock phrases. Strategic and brand material scores highest — the [rebrand's 'as written' signature](narr:Assess_Phrasing_rebrand), the [IP-crisis metaphor cluster](narr:Assessment_Phrasing_IPCrisis) ('IP as code', 'deepest lever'), the [GTM signature phrases](narr:RubricAssess_Phrasing_GTM), and the [Jan-7 voice-memo idiolect](narr:RubricAssess_Phrasing_20260107). A [core rubric assessment](narr:RubricAssess_Phrasing) catalogs the canonical metaphors ('narrative architecture', 'steering vector', 'resonant body') and notes deliberate self-correction. Multiple children attribute distinct voices to named speakers — [the customer's chief architect's verbs](narr:Assessment_Phrasing_CustomerArchitect), [Tony's call markers](narr:RubricAssess_Phrasing_TonyCall), an infrastructure advisor's infrastructure phrasing. Against this, the technical-documentation assessments read flatter: [the cm doc](narr:Assess_Phrasing_cm) and [collective-memory doc](narr:Assess_Phrasing_collective_memory) report consistent terminology but only generic stock phrases. The span is consistent terminology → strong branded idiolect → conversational authenticity, dated where transcripts carry dates.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#Assess_Phrasing_cm> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#Assess_Phrasing_collective_memory> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#Assess_Phrasing_rebrand> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#Assessment_Phrasing_1> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#Assessment_Phrasing_IPCrisis> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#Assessment_Phrasing_CustomerArchitect> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#RubricAssess_Phrasing> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#RubricAssess_Phrasing_1> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#RubricAssess_Phrasing_20260107> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#RubricAssess_Phrasing_ADR001> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#RubricAssess_Phrasing_ADR002> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#RubricAssess_Phrasing_GTM> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#RubricAssess_Phrasing_TonyCall> ;
